column4: Twas insult that lead to injury, twas injury that lead to more insults... Twas these insults that lead to Microsoft and Mac....For years this circle went 'round and 'round, but now Ubuntu's come to town... With Open-Source, we'll rule the world, UBUNTU LINUX BOYS AND GIRLS!!!
::bow:: Thank you, thank you, I'll be here all week :P
not with that attitude, you won't
